description: Keep ahead of your game with this light, versatile hunting vest in safety orange. The camouflage print blends in well in bushland, making you difficult for animals to detect yet highly visible for your hunting team. Easy to pull over other hunting garments and takes up little space in your backpack when not in use. Stretch panels in the sides for a great fit and pockets for a radio and things you want close at hand.
name: Fjallraven Varmland Vest
